STEAMVR AND XR Setup: 
Step 1: Go to Edit -> Project Settings -> XR PlugIn Management -> Plug-In Providers -> Check OpenXR
(You have to install XR PlugIn Management or it will ask you install PlugIn Managament when you open XR PlugIn Management.)
(Install XR PlugIn Management from Package Manager)
Step 2: Install XR Interaction Toolkit Package
Step 3: OpenXR PlugIn Package
Step 4: Go to Asset Store and Download SteamVR PlugIn
Step 5: When you go to Project Settings -> PlugIn Management -> Plug-In Providers -> OpenXR and OpenVR Loader will be checked.
